{"tid":425513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"解放33C咪咪！范文雅越南引仔追","createTime":"2017-10-05T19:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T06:30:58.000Z","uid":141962,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"964ab53f06ac1c5d25acf72059d01984226446b4","tid":425513,"uid":141962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T19:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033653_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033653_cdc679bebbe282e170ab6fe0dca8445e.jpg&h=0ede3dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033654_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033654_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=f2d1f67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033654_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033654_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=9132122a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033748_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033748_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=4857d5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫「咪神」輩出，華姐出身的范文雅（Aliya）曾在旅遊節目《3日2夜》中穿泳衣騷Quali，最近客串處境劇《開心速遞》飾演設計師CoCo，穿上緊身裙色誘歐瑞偉，玲瓏浮凸身材令她在網上人氣急升，網友紛紛封她做最索Body！<br />\n<br />\n努力改善身材<br />\n<br />\n早前Aliya忙裏偷閒到越南旅行，除了解放游水自拍，又在房間拍下唯美床照，白滑肌膚加C Cup牛奶胸大為搶Fo！她說：「夏天冇曬過，咪帶多啲泳衣，最近又學緊影相，好多相都係自己Set機影。」身高1米72，三圍33C、23、34的Aliya仍謙稱身形未夠好，要努力改善：「同其他女仔比就冇咩信心，公司好多女仔都好瘦，我有啲肥肥哋，依家每朝都會飲五青汁，同埋多做瑜伽。」<br />\n<br />\n索爆的Aliya在澳洲長大，此行有艷遇引來「同鄉」澳洲男撩傾偈及交換Contact，她說：「當時喺酒店個Bar飲嘢，媽咪幫我影相，但效果麻麻，個澳洲男士就過嚟幫我影，佢讚我Cute同靚女，畀咗Facebook我，仲話自己唔係成日撩女仔喎！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033748_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033748_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=eea581b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033748_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033748_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=ff870571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/033748_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F033748_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=e01180ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171006/bkn-20171006000047568-1006_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171006%2Fbkn-20171006000047568-1006_00862_001.html&d=iZJlOYnniq6LZk5pHvb61Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b5dbd193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171006/bkn-20171006000047568-1006_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f8d98ba59890f4cec078c2436d26a2c280a67722","tid":425513,"uid":3161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T20:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/043639_cb4e206424f7b7789eed393c02dca228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F043639_cb4e206424f7b7789eed393c02dca228.jpg&h=95eabc10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"204e7abc21371624fbbba48167b9fd96488bb6bf","tid":425513,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"食洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma